#Province/State contain 100% null values
#Categories are filled with Mode and numeric values are filled with Mean

#filling null values
for i in df.columns:
    if df[i].dtypes==object:
        df[i]=df[i].fillna(df[i].mode()[0])
    else:
        df[i]=df[i].fillna(df[i].mean())

    else:
        con.append(i)

print('Con columns: ',con)
